<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px;">为了给同学们营造一个良好的学习环境，培养同学们的志愿服务精神，发扬当代青年乐于奉献、开拓进取的精神风貌，让雷锋精神吹遍校园每一个角落，我校于1月4日至5日期间举办了“志愿红迎接新年红，我为同学做实事”志愿服务活动。在这一天半的时间里，江软志愿者们共搬运图书12万册，完成了这项艰巨的任务。同时在这次活动中，退役军人学院、智能科技学院、VR 与艺术学院、信息技术学院军教大队、校教官连、校学生会以及青年志愿者协会等组织给予了大力支持。他们积极参与，全力以赴，为活动的顺利开展做出了重要贡献。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.4pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A30%3A08%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132845.jpg?Expires=2019965409&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=uOknlDvGJBKB2DhCApTJFCO%2B22I%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29.4pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A30%3A24%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132852.jpg?Expires=2019965424&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=7%2BEuPum4jXZBS%2FLiBrlXPMB9vt4%3D" alt="" width="650" height="538" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 6pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29.4pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px;">搬运和摆放工作在现场负责人的指引下有条不紊地进行。工作人员首先从搬运地点、运送方式和人员分配等方面做了介绍和要求，然后志愿者们根据图书馆书籍搬运的工作内容和要求，分成两个小组同时开展工作：一组人员负责将书籍从仓库装车运送至新图书馆，另一组人员负责将书籍按照类别分好，并有序地搬运至书架。志愿者们之间密切配合、团结合作，一起为打造崭新整洁的阅读环境而努力。整个现场分工明确、秩序井然，志愿者们穿梭其中，有条不紊地进行工作。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29.4pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A30%3A49%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132905.jpg?Expires=2019965450&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=77rlZe9GTsFDLbyOx1ybA02Kvys%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.4pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22.2pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px;">在这次与书籍的零距离接触中，志愿者们忘却了工作的劳累，积极热情地参与其中，这应该就是雷锋精神所给予的力量。搬运活动的辛苦，不仅助力了图书馆的休整和管理，也提高了同学们的志愿服务意识和责任感。让同学们对奉献精神有了更深刻的体会，展现了当代大学生积极投身志愿服务的风采，为校园环境的美化和精神文明建设做出了应有的贡献。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22.2pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 22.2pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A31%3A12%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132916.jpg?Expires=2019965472&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=iFrXllqOO5Bcfcad0a9RzFGo9ZY%3D" alt="" width="650" height="487" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22.2pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px;">志愿红迎接新年红，我为同学做实事。此次志愿服务活动正是因为有了这些组织和同学们的支持和参与，才能够取得如此圆满的成功。江软学子用实际行动诠释了“奉献、友爱、互助、进步”的志愿服务精神，展现了当代大学生良好的精神风貌。在此，我们向所有参与本次活动的组织和个人表示衷心的感谢和敬意！希望在今后的日子里，我们能够继续携手共进，为学校的发展做出更大的贡献！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A31%3A30%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132927.jpg?Expires=2019965490&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=lT%2FWD%2BVqmLxcIqAeKkhuID0YbaQ%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 86, 86); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-07%2013%3A31%3A45%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240107132911.jpg?Expires=2019965506&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=m2mbvil%2BVE%2BgN0pYvEWqMO1RxMA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p><br/></p>